kuthi abalandeli bemidlalo yeshashalazi baphume bebusisekile ePlayhouse Opera lapho kuzobe kunomdlalo ohambisana nomculo, iMaria! Telling The Story of The Son, obophele izihlabani zabalingisi kanye nabaculi phakathi kwabo okubalwa uBrian Temba azobe edlala indawo ephambili kanye noYolanda Myeza. Lomdlalo owethulwe yiWorld Gospel Powerhouse ngaphansi kwesandla sikaZanele LaMbokazi Nkambule uxoxa ngempilo kaJesu. Kulindeleke ukuthi uqale ngoLwesihlanu, Ephreli 15 uphele ngoMsombuluko,  Ephreli 18.  NgoLwesihlanu nangakusasa ngoMgqibelo kuqalwa ngo-7 ebusuku, bese kuthi ngeSonto nangoMsombuluko kuqalwa ngo-3ntambama. Amathikithi okubuka lomdlalo aseyatholakala ezikhungweni ezawadayisayo.